dcterms:description: SemanticKITTI is a large-scale dataset for semantic scene understanding using LiDAR sequences, based on the KITTI Vision Benchmark, with dense semantic annotation for the entire KITTI Odometry Benchmark, presenting challenges on rare classes due to limited training examples.
dcterms:title: SemanticKITTI
